---
title: Apricot-Glazed Lamb Chops with Spring Veggies and Creamy Smashed Potatoes
description: Zippy whole grain mustard and apricot spread come together to make a luscious glaze that brings out the lamb's natural sweetness in this festive, delicious dish!
